INSERT INTO codigosAcessoGestante (gestanteId, codigo, destino, expiraEm, createdAt)
SELECT 
  id,
  '999999' as codigo,
  'teste@gestantesapp.com',
  DATE_ADD(NOW(), INTERVAL 60 MINUTE),
  NOW()
FROM gestantes 
WHERE email = 'teste@gestantesapp.com'
LIMIT 1;

SELECT 'USE ESTE CÓDIGO: 999999' as mensagem, expiraEm, 'VÁLIDO POR 60 MINUTOS' as status
FROM codigosAcessoGestante 
WHERE codigo = '999999' AND destino = 'teste@gestantesapp.com'
ORDER BY createdAt DESC 
LIMIT 1;
